column5: My daughter booked Killarney PP for our camping trip this summer in late August. Any recommendations for things to do in the area? Fun off the beaten path type things. Also, What should I expect as far as fishing. Mostly  Smallmouth ? Do I bring the boat  or canoe ? Thanks
That park brings back memories from my 20's. The activities then are not family oriented, making a family maybe. Have fun. it is beautiful there, it was 40 years ago.
